The problem is: ``while(true);``

Your minimal Win32 program needs to include a &#39;message pump&#39; after you create &amp; show the window:

```
    // Main message loop
    MSG msg = {};
    while (WM_QUIT != msg.message)
    {
        if (PeekMessage(&amp;msg, nullptr, 0, 0, PM_REMOVE))
        {
            TranslateMessage(&amp;msg);
            DispatchMessage(&amp;msg);
        }
    }
```

